1
00:01:10,880 --> 00:01:11,880
Judging by your attire,

2
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:13,159
you must be from the Bureau of Imperial Attire.

3
00:01:13,520 --> 00:01:15,879
A mere palace maid dares to kill at midnight

4
00:01:15,879 --> 00:01:17,079
and dump the body in a well.

5
00:01:17,360 --> 00:01:18,720
Do you know this is a capital crime?

6
00:01:19,599 --> 00:01:22,079
Judging by your attire, you are not from the palace.

7
00:01:22,599 --> 00:01:25,439
An outside male in the harem during curfew.

8
00:01:25,439 --> 00:01:27,320
Do you know that is also a capital crime?

9
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:29,120
This little palace maid isn't panicked at all.

10
00:01:29,159 --> 00:01:30,359
She even retorts.

11
00:01:31,359 --> 00:01:33,760
Should I acknowledge A-Xuan?

12
00:01:33,839 --> 00:01:35,199
Since you have discovered me,

13
00:01:35,199 --> 00:01:36,399
I might as well do as you did.

14
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:37,920
Kill the witness.

15
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:43,280
You left evidence even while dumping a body.

16
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,560
You are far too careless.

17
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:47,999
Palace rules are strict.

18
00:01:48,039 --> 00:01:49,079
Private sacrifices

19
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,240
are punishable by death.

20
00:01:50,799 --> 00:01:52,039
If My Lord is willing to let me go,

21
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:54,200
I will pretend I never saw this evidence.

22
00:01:54,439 --> 00:01:56,320
Tonight, we stay out of each other's way.

23
00:01:56,359 --> 00:01:57,320
We owe each other nothing.

24
00:01:57,320 --> 00:01:58,039
What do you say?

25
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,280
This palace maid...

26
00:01:59,479 --> 00:02:01,079
she doesn't flinch in the face of death.

27
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:02,240
She dares to threaten others.

28
00:02:02,359 --> 00:02:03,679
She actually has quite the courage.

29
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:04,640
Forget it.

30
00:02:04,880 --> 00:02:06,479
He will be returning to the army soon.

31
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,600
Better not let him wade into this muddy water.

32
00:02:08,920 --> 00:02:10,719
You want to threaten me with a scrap of paper?

33
00:02:10,999 --> 00:02:12,160
Do you know who I am?

34
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:16,880
The guards outside will search here soon.

35
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:19,080
If I shout and attract them here...

36
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,279
My Lord,

37
00:02:20,639 --> 00:02:22,000
that pot of sacrificial fire

38
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:23,479
hasn't completely gone out yet, has it?

39
00:02:29,919 --> 00:02:31,039
Cheap tricks.

40
00:02:31,039 --> 00:02:32,160
Trying to scheme against me.

41
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,479
My Lord has misunderstood.

42
00:02:33,679 --> 00:02:34,960
Since neither of us trusts the other,

43
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,240
let us hold leverage over each other.

44
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:38,880
Consider us in the same boat.

45
00:02:39,199 --> 00:02:39,919
My Lord,

46
00:02:39,919 --> 00:02:41,759
do not do anything that harms others without benefiting yourself.

47
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:46,520
That... boatmate...

48
00:02:46,919 --> 00:02:47,759
how should I address you?

49
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:51,240
Feng Qing.

50
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,839
It is simple for someone to die in this palace,

51
00:02:53,839 --> 00:02:54,880
yet also not simple.

52
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:57,160
Especially a eunuch from the Directorate of Ceremonial.

53
00:02:57,399 --> 00:02:58,839
Survive this ordeal first,

54
00:02:59,039 --> 00:03:01,199
then you will be qualified to be in the same boat with me.

55
00:03:08,119 --> 00:03:09,919
Was this paper money burned for me?

56
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:13,839
The boy who always followed behind me in childhood...

57
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:16,080
when did he become so fierce?

58
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,079
Director Chen.

59
00:03:23,239 --> 00:03:24,479
Why are you here so late?

60
00:03:24,919 --> 00:03:26,359
This slave came to ask you, Director,

61
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,000
when to deliver the Ceremonial Robe tomorrow.

62
00:03:30,039 --> 00:03:31,320
By the looks of it,

63
00:03:31,519 --> 00:03:33,039
you served him well.

64
00:03:34,919 --> 00:03:36,680
This face is born to seduce.

65
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:38,759
No wonder Eunuch Sun likes it.

66
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,280
Those sent before...

67
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:42,079
those little wenches pretending to be high and mighty,

68
00:03:42,079 --> 00:03:43,239
none were of any use.

69
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:44,680
You are the sensible one.

70
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:48,039
Chastity is not as important as one's life.

71
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,639
Tomorrow at the Hour of Mao,

72
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:51,000
come with me to deliver the Ceremonial Robe.

73
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,840
Once Noble Consort Meng is satisfied,

74
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:55,519
and Eunuch Sun puts in a good word for me,

75
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:58,479
my bright future will be within reach.

76
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:04,880
So it was you who lured Eunuch Sun here.

77
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:06,919
Then on his way to the Yellow Springs,

78
00:04:07,519 --> 00:04:09,560
how could he lack a villain like you to be buried with him?

79
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,799
It was made quite quickly.

80
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:21,280
The Bureau of Imperial Attire has not disappointed me.

81
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:23,000
Reward them.

82
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:23,639
Yes.

83
00:04:23,759 --> 00:04:24,959
Thank you, My Lady.

84
00:04:33,639 --> 00:04:35,160
The Nine-Phoenix and Pheasant Pattern

85
00:04:35,479 --> 00:04:36,840
This is reserved for the Empress.

86
00:04:36,919 --> 00:04:38,280
You have some nerve.

87
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:40,000
No.

88
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:41,239
I knew nothing about this.

89
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:42,320
Impossible.

90
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:48,560
It has been a long time since I did needlework.

91
00:04:48,959 --> 00:04:50,440
Even my skills have become unsteady.

92
00:04:51,280 --> 00:04:53,759
The one who taught the Bureau of Imperial Attire to embroider the Nine-Phoenix and Pheasant Pattern back then...

93
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:56,199
...was none other than these hands of mine.

94
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:57,280
Impossible.

95
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,199
My Lady.

96
00:04:58,519 --> 00:05:00,120
I have been in the palace for twenty years.

97
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:02,440
How could I not know that violating dress code is a capital crime?

98
00:05:02,519 --> 00:05:03,959
I am innocent!

99
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:04,959
Innocent?

100
00:05:05,359 --> 00:05:07,799
Did this pattern grow on there by itself?

101
00:05:08,359 --> 00:05:09,160
It was you.

102
00:05:09,239 --> 00:05:11,000
I checked the Ceremonial Robe last night at the Hour of Hai.

103
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:11,919
After that...

104
00:05:11,919 --> 00:05:13,079
...I only saw you.

105
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,000
I am innocent.

106
00:05:17,239 --> 00:05:19,320
This is the first time I've seen this Ceremonial Robe today.

107
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:19,959
You!

108
00:05:19,959 --> 00:05:20,919
Last night in the weaving room...

109
00:05:20,919 --> 00:05:23,120
...you must have embroidered the pattern later to frame me!

110
00:05:23,199 --> 00:05:24,000
You lowly maid!

111
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:24,440
I...

112
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:25,120
Enough.

113
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:35,240
You are the one who delivered the Ceremonial Robe to Lanzhi Palace that day.

114
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:36,880
It was indeed me.

115
00:05:37,839 --> 00:05:38,880
My Lady, please see the truth.

116
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:41,839
The Late Empress designed this Nine-Phoenix and Pheasant Pattern herself.

117
00:05:42,159 --> 00:05:44,320
Only the Director of the Bureau of Imperial Attire knows how to embroider it.

118
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,880
I am just a lowly palace maid.

119
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:46,680
How could I possibly embroider it?

120
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:47,519
It was you!

121
00:05:47,759 --> 00:05:48,560
My Lady.

122
00:05:48,639 --> 00:05:50,040
It was this lowly maid who did it!

123
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,159
My Lady.

124
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:56,040
Director Chen holds an official position, after all.

125
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:58,759
Why don't we execute that palace maid first...

126
00:05:58,759 --> 00:06:00,079
...to give Noble Consort Meng an explanation?

127
00:06:07,519 --> 00:06:09,680
Director, I could die unjustly for you.

128
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:11,240
But for a beheading offense like this...

129
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,639
...if we say I did it...

130
00:06:12,759 --> 00:06:13,800
...who would believe it?

131
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,480
You...

132
00:06:15,519 --> 00:06:16,839
Killing a palace maid...

133
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:19,240
...do you take Noble Consort Meng for a fool?

134
00:06:19,839 --> 00:06:20,959
Besides, on that day...

135
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,800
...it was this maid who persuaded Noble Consort Meng...

136
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,920
...to agree to remake the Ceremonial Robe...

137
00:06:25,159 --> 00:06:26,560
...and calmed her anger.

138
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,240
My Lady sees everything clearly.

139
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:32,000
If you hadn't understood the situation...

140
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,560
...even if I had a hundred mouths...

141
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,800
...I wouldn't be able to explain myself.

142
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:35,519
You...

143
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:39,440
As the Director of the Bureau of Imperial Attire...

144
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:41,680
...you made and kept the Ceremonial Robe.

145
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,040
Now that something has gone wrong...

146
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:44,759
...you cannot escape responsibility no matter what.

147
00:06:45,199 --> 00:06:46,800
And now you try to implicate others.

148
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:49,159
It clearly shows your treacherous intent.

149
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:50,599
My Lady, spare my life!

150
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:51,599
My Lady!

151
00:06:51,639 --> 00:06:52,759
My Lady, spare me!

152
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:54,519
It really wasn't me, My Lady!

153
00:06:54,599 --> 00:06:56,040
My Lady! My Lady!

154
00:06:56,440 --> 00:06:57,240
My Lady!

155
00:06:57,279 --> 00:06:59,399
My Lady, spare me! It wasn't me!

156
00:07:06,199 --> 00:07:07,839
My Lady, I am innocent!

157
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,279
My Lady, someone framed me!

158
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:15,240
My Lady! My Lady, spare my life!

159
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,719
Spare me!

160
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:23,680
It was you.

161
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:24,920
It was you!

162
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:27,000
You framed me!

163
00:07:28,199 --> 00:07:29,719
Do you realize now...

164
00:07:30,159 --> 00:07:31,440
...between innocence and life...

165
00:07:31,839 --> 00:07:32,839
...which is more important?

166
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:38,560
My Lady, someone framed me!

167
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,079
So much noise.

168
00:07:40,279 --> 00:07:41,360
You are disturbing My Lady's peace.

169
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,519
Strangle her to death.

170
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,399
My Lady!

171
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:47,719
Director Chen.

172
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,199
You have done much evil.

173
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:51,040
I will now send you on your way.

174
00:08:06,959 --> 00:08:08,639
The harem is full of hidden dangers.

175
00:08:09,279 --> 00:08:10,880
My status is lowly right now.

176
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,920
I must first protect my own life...

177
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:15,639
...to have a chance to investigate the fire.

178
00:08:28,079 --> 00:08:29,279
The fire was definitely not an accident.

179
00:08:30,079 --> 00:08:31,079
I wonder if here...

180
00:08:31,599 --> 00:08:33,199
...there might be some clues left behind.

181
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:49,000
My Lady, what's wrong?

182
00:08:49,839 --> 00:08:50,599
Yinsheng.

183
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,880
Go pour me a cup of water.

184
00:08:53,519 --> 00:08:54,240
Yes.

185
00:08:56,719 --> 00:08:58,519
That knockout incense only drains my strength.

186
00:08:59,279 --> 00:09:01,079
If the mastermind set a death trap,

187
00:09:01,639 --> 00:09:03,399
there should be a backup plan to kill me.

188
00:09:08,639 --> 00:09:10,560
I didn't go near that candle stand back then.

189
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:12,240
How did it fall over?

190
00:09:13,079 --> 00:09:14,399
There must be something strange about it.

191
00:09:16,639 --> 00:09:18,000
Since there are no other clues,

192
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:20,240
I'll start by investigating the origin of this incense.

193
00:09:21,199 --> 00:09:22,759
It might lead me to the culprit.

194
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:31,560
Noble Consort Leng,

195
00:09:31,759 --> 00:09:33,360
you've been kneeling for hours.

196
00:09:33,519 --> 00:09:34,959
Your body can't take this.

197
00:09:37,959 --> 00:09:38,599
My Lady.

198
00:09:40,199 --> 00:09:41,000
Your Majesty.

199
00:09:41,279 --> 00:09:43,640
Noble Consort Leng, regarding the introduction of the mage,

200
00:09:43,640 --> 00:09:44,959
is outside pleading for forgiveness.

201
00:09:45,239 --> 00:09:48,040
She's been kneeling in the scorching sun for half the day.

202
00:09:48,800 --> 00:09:50,599
If she likes to kneel, let her kneel.

203
00:09:51,119 --> 00:09:52,199
I want to see

204
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,239
just how sincere she is.

205
00:09:56,719 --> 00:09:57,520
My Lady.

206
00:10:08,119 --> 00:10:09,640
I summoned you here to ask...

207
00:10:10,119 --> 00:10:12,359
The internal service has been somewhat lacking lately.

208
00:10:12,959 --> 00:10:13,879
Have you noticed?

209
00:10:14,719 --> 00:10:17,320
The food sent by the Food Bureau is rather plain.

210
00:10:18,040 --> 00:10:19,520
The stitching from the Bureau of Imperial Attire, too...

211
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:24,079
If my elder sister were still here,

212
00:10:24,239 --> 00:10:26,079
the harem would surely be in perfect order.

213
00:10:26,719 --> 00:10:28,920
It is a pity Wan'er cannot share Your Majesty's burdens.

214
00:10:30,280 --> 00:10:31,800
Do you also wish to emulate your sister...

215
00:10:32,199 --> 00:10:33,239
and become Empress?

216
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,800
I would never dare harbor such thoughts.

217
00:10:36,479 --> 00:10:37,839
My elder sister cared for the whole world.

218
00:10:37,999 --> 00:10:39,199
Wan'er is far from her equal.

219
00:10:40,479 --> 00:10:42,239
Wan'er's heart follows only Your Majesty.

220
00:10:42,959 --> 00:10:44,320
I just do not know what to do...

221
00:10:44,719 --> 00:10:46,719
to relieve Your Majesty's worries and fatigue.

222
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:50,479
Now that the Central Palace is vacant...

223
00:10:51,119 --> 00:10:52,160
and the Six Palaces await management,

224
00:10:52,560 --> 00:10:55,680
are you willing to take charge of the Seal of the Phoenix...

225
00:10:57,680 --> 00:10:59,199
and temporarily manage the harem's affairs?

226
00:11:03,999 --> 00:11:05,040
I am terrified by the honor.

227
00:11:05,079 --> 00:11:06,359
Thanks to Your Majesty's favor,

228
00:11:06,719 --> 00:11:08,119
I will do my utmost...

229
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:09,400
not to fail your grace.

230
00:11:12,160 --> 00:11:13,320
As for the Imperial Sericulture Rite,

231
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:15,440
you must organize it well.

232
00:11:20,239 --> 00:11:21,119
Your Majesty.

233
00:11:21,999 --> 00:11:23,599
Lord Gu Xuan requests an audience.

234
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:30,040
Your subject Gu Xuan greets Your Majesty, Imperial Noble Consort Wan.

235
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:32,560
You and I were educated together since childhood.

236
00:11:32,920 --> 00:11:34,199
Why stand on such ceremony?

237
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:36,520
I returned to the capital without an imperial decree.

238
00:11:36,760 --> 00:11:38,920
Having heard of the deaths of my aunt and elder sister...

239
00:11:39,359 --> 00:11:40,839
even if I must face death for disobeying orders,

240
00:11:40,839 --> 00:11:42,079
I had to rush back.

241
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:43,479
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.

242
00:11:43,999 --> 00:11:45,520
Encountering such sudden misfortune...

243
00:11:46,079 --> 00:11:48,479
how could I punish you for returning without orders?

244
00:11:48,719 --> 00:11:49,999
My sister was the Empress...

245
00:11:50,520 --> 00:11:52,239
yet she was burned alive in the palace.

246
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:54,479
My grief is truly hard to quell.

247
00:11:55,999 --> 00:11:57,440
When you went north with the army years ago...

248
00:11:57,920 --> 00:11:58,800
before you left,

249
00:11:59,359 --> 00:12:00,400
I promised you...

250
00:12:00,640 --> 00:12:02,040
that I would take good care of the Late Empress.

251
00:12:02,599 --> 00:12:03,760
Your behavior now...

252
00:12:04,199 --> 00:12:05,959
are you blaming me for not caring for her well?

253
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,599
With my elder sister's passing,

254
00:12:10,599 --> 00:12:12,280
Your Majesty must also be heartbroken.

255
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:13,640
But the fire was merciless.

256
00:12:13,999 --> 00:12:15,640
How can one blame Your Majesty?

257
00:12:17,119 --> 00:12:18,479
Regarding the fire that took the Late Empress...

258
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:21,040
I will surely give you siblings an explanation.

259
00:12:22,879 --> 00:12:24,119
Thank you for your grace, Your Majesty.

260
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:28,999
Your Majesty.

261
00:12:29,520 --> 00:12:30,999
Second Sister has always been frail and afraid of the cold.

262
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,119
Now that our elder sister is gone,

263
00:12:33,800 --> 00:12:35,359
I implore Your Majesty to grant permission...

264
00:12:35,680 --> 00:12:36,959
to allow me to stay in the palace temporarily...

265
00:12:36,959 --> 00:12:38,440
to nurse the Noble Consort's health.

266
00:12:38,920 --> 00:12:40,280
You have studied medical texts since childhood...

267
00:12:40,520 --> 00:12:41,999
and saved lives in the army.

268
00:12:42,520 --> 00:12:44,760
You haven't neglected your skills all these years.

269
00:12:45,839 --> 00:12:46,680
From this day forth,

270
00:12:47,119 --> 00:12:48,280
you shall serve in the Imperial Medical Bureau...

271
00:12:49,079 --> 00:12:50,440
and take good care of your sister.

272
00:12:50,719 --> 00:12:51,599
Many thanks, Your Majesty.

273
00:12:53,760 --> 00:12:55,560
Imperial Noble Consort Wan now holds the Seal of the Phoenix.

274
00:12:55,599 --> 00:12:56,520
She has many duties.

275
00:12:56,920 --> 00:12:58,199
Go back and rest early.

276
00:12:58,680 --> 00:12:59,599
Thank you, Your Majesty.

277
00:13:03,119 --> 00:13:04,119
Your subject takes his leave.

278
00:13:06,160 --> 00:13:07,800
Do you think kneeling outside the hall for so long...

279
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:10,199
will exempt you from punishment?

280
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:11,359
I would not dare think so.

281
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:13,879
The Late Empress died in the mourning hall fire.

282
00:13:14,479 --> 00:13:16,760
Those involved are guilty beyond forgiveness.

283
00:13:17,119 --> 00:13:19,560
The monk praying for blessings is especially to blame.

284
00:13:19,839 --> 00:13:20,920
His crime warrants death by a thousand cuts.

285
00:13:20,920 --> 00:13:22,879
No, it is not so, Your Majesty.

286
00:13:23,560 --> 00:13:25,239
I was the one who recommended the monk.

287
00:13:25,479 --> 00:13:27,160
I am willing to bear all the blame.

288
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:28,520
I ask to be sent to the Cold Palace.

289
00:13:28,959 --> 00:13:31,199
I only beg you to spare the monk from a capital crime.

290
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:34,160
Consider it a prayer for Her Highness.

291
00:13:35,239 --> 00:13:36,599
I ask to enter the Cold Palace.

292
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:39,560
After the Late Empress passed away,

293
00:13:40,560 --> 00:13:42,719
I have chanted sutras for her every day.

294
00:13:45,680 --> 00:13:47,320
Since it is to pray for the Late Empress,

295
00:13:48,920 --> 00:13:49,959
then I shall grant it.

296
00:13:50,359 --> 00:13:51,599
I spare the monk from the capital crime...

297
00:13:52,719 --> 00:13:54,999
and order him to keep vigil for the Late Empress.

298
00:13:57,400 --> 00:13:58,199
As for you,

299
00:13:59,239 --> 00:14:01,320
go to the Cold Palace to chant sutras for the Late Empress.

300
00:14:02,040 --> 00:14:05,359
You may not step out unless summoned.

301
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:10,479
I accept the decree with gratitude.

302
00:14:19,719 --> 00:14:21,359
Everything has two sides.

303
00:14:21,999 --> 00:14:23,280
Fortune and misfortune are intertwined.

304
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:25,800
Using one person's shackles

305
00:14:26,839 --> 00:14:28,400
to save a hundred lives.

306
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,199
Fortunately.

307
00:14:32,760 --> 00:14:33,640
Fortunately.

308
00:14:43,680 --> 00:14:44,959
The Empress is dead.

309
00:14:45,040 --> 00:14:47,199
The Gu family only has the frail Gu Wan left.

310
00:14:47,560 --> 00:14:50,199
Everyone in the court said I should succeed as Empress.

311
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,520
But look at things now.

312
00:14:51,839 --> 00:14:53,839
Not only did she preside over the Imperial Sericulture Rite,

313
00:14:53,959 --> 00:14:55,400
she also holds the Seal of the Phoenix.

314
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:56,239
The Seal of the Phoenix.

315
00:14:56,760 --> 00:14:58,199
Do you know what that means?

316
00:14:59,280 --> 00:15:01,479
First, the Ceremonial Robe allergy plan was botched.

317
00:15:01,920 --> 00:15:03,719
Forcing me to go to Lanzhi Palace myself

318
00:15:03,719 --> 00:15:04,879
to seize the Imperial Sericulture Rite.

319
00:15:05,479 --> 00:15:07,280
Then the dress the Bureau of Imperial Attire rushed to make

320
00:15:07,280 --> 00:15:08,440
also had issues.

321
00:15:08,839 --> 00:15:11,079
You think disposing of a Director settles it?

322
00:15:11,640 --> 00:15:12,719
My Lady, please understand.

323
00:15:13,560 --> 00:15:14,839
The dress violated regulations.

324
00:15:15,119 --> 00:15:16,320
It was a capital crime.

325
00:15:16,520 --> 00:15:18,040
I worried she would implicate you, My Lady.

326
00:15:18,040 --> 00:15:19,400
So I had her beaten to death.

327
00:15:19,520 --> 00:15:21,719
Only the dead do not talk, My Lady.

328
00:15:21,719 --> 00:15:23,560
Then why didn't you interrogate her strictly?

329
00:15:23,839 --> 00:15:25,520
Make her implicate that witch, Gu Wan.

330
00:15:26,239 --> 00:15:28,959
That would have removed a thorn in my side.

331
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:31,320
Since Director Chen did this,

332
00:15:31,839 --> 00:15:33,280
she must have been ready to die.

333
00:15:33,359 --> 00:15:35,320
Even if someone instructed her from behind the scenes,

334
00:15:35,560 --> 00:15:36,999
she likely wouldn't have confessed.

335
00:15:39,400 --> 00:15:40,719
Is that really so?

336
00:15:41,719 --> 00:15:42,719
Concubine Cao.

337
00:15:44,119 --> 00:15:45,400
You killed her.

338
00:15:45,719 --> 00:15:47,440
Did you not have any selfish motives?

339
00:15:53,040 --> 00:15:55,959
My Lady, even if I had the nerve of the heavens,

340
00:15:55,959 --> 00:15:57,959
I would never dare betray you.

341
00:15:58,160 --> 00:15:59,440
Because of the Ceremonial Robe,

342
00:15:59,680 --> 00:16:00,999
all my previous preparations

343
00:16:00,999 --> 00:16:02,239
have fallen short.

344
00:16:03,040 --> 00:16:05,640
Watching that witch bask in glory...

345
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:10,199
...is something I simply cannot swallow.

346
00:16:16,160 --> 00:16:17,400
Rest assured, My Lady.

347
00:16:17,599 --> 00:16:20,239
If I don't find the truth within three days,

348
00:16:20,400 --> 00:16:22,599
I will accept any punishment.

349
00:16:29,999 --> 00:16:31,400
In my rules,

350
00:16:31,800 --> 00:16:33,239
useless people don't deserve to live.

351
00:16:34,520 --> 00:16:36,239
I give you one day to investigate.

352
00:16:36,760 --> 00:16:39,119
I want to know who is behind this.

353
00:16:43,560 --> 00:16:44,800
Bring them to me alive,

354
00:16:45,079 --> 00:16:46,320
or bring me the corpse.

355
00:16:47,239 --> 00:16:48,119
Do you understand?

356
00:16:50,280 --> 00:16:50,959
Yes.
